These are Puzzles for 7x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, december
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: weightlifting, sailing
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, rose
House: ranch-style, townhouse
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: swisher, alhambra
There 2 different types of food: avocado, kiwi
City: edinburgh, san-francisco
1. the person who's birthday is in october is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsrose is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
4. the person eating avocado is the alhambra-smoker##1
5. the townhouse house is on the far left##1
6. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person traveling to san-francisco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |
| Birthday      | december     | october       |
| Sport         | weightlifting   | sailing     |
| Flower           | marigold | rose   |
| House   | townhouse   | ranch-style  |
| Cigar   | alhambra | swisher |
| Food           | avocado      | kiwi     |
| City     | san-francisco    | edinburgh   |

