.:: Puzzle 7x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, coral
House: ranch-style, victorian
There 2 different types of food: pineapple, corn
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, november
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: rose, amaryllis
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: comedy, western
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: basketball, badminton
1. the person eating corn is on the right of the victorian house##1
2. the person watching western movies is the person who's sport is badminton##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far right##1
5. the person who likes ivory is the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Color      | ivory    | coral |
| House         | victorian        | ranch-style  |
| Food           | pineapple | corn  |
| Birthday   | november            | january    |
| Flower   | rose     | amaryllis   |
| Movie-Genre           | comedy         | western    |
| Sport     | basketball           | badminton      |

