2. the person who's birthday is in january is on the right of the art-deco house##1
3. the nigerian is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the right of the fan of dubstep##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2      |
| Birthday      | june          | january       |
