3. the person playing backgammon is on the far right##1
4. the person driving the car is on the far left##1
5. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the palace house is the person who likes chestnut##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |
| Sport      | water-polo      | surfing          |
| Game          | scrabble   | backgammon      |
